<section id="spillane">

<h1 class="section__header">Mickey Spillane</h1>

<div class="columns-spillane">

<p class="secondary">Frank Morrison Spillane was an American author of crime novels, many featuring his signature detective character, Mike Hammer. More than 225 million copies of his books have sold internationally. When literary critics had a negative reaction to Spillane&#8217;s writing&#8212;citing the high content of sex and violence&#8212;Spillane answered with a few terse comments: &#8220;Those big-shot writers could never dig the fact that there are more salted peanuts consumed than caviar&#8230;&#8221; If the public likes you, you're good.&#8221;</p>

</div><!-- columns -->

